name: 特里斯顿·戴伊
name_full: 特里斯顿·戴伊 Triston Dye
introduction: Triston Mitchell Dye, an actor born in 1998 in Tulsa, Oklahoma, was raised in Durango, Colorado and moved to Atlanta, Georgia in 2017.Once in Atlanta, he quickly landed parts in Point Man (2018), Homicide Hunter (2019), Full Count (2019), and Dead Silent (2020), as well as over twenty short films. Post 2021, he booked roles in Disney's Just Beyond (2021), Talk Black (2022), Landscape with Invisible Hand (2023), the hit television series Atlanta Season 3 (2022), and Marvel's Ironheart (2023).He is now shooting Season 8 of Fear the Walking Dead in Savannah, GA.
